snippet.title: Autumn Amber Ale Tasting (First All Grain Batch!), New Equipment, Plus a Shout Out!
snippet.description: Howdy everyone!  WHEW!  Well, it has come time to taste my first all grain batch of brew... I was sweating it!  Also, I have a very sincere shout out for hophedbrewhaus for his great all grain videos, as well as a thanks for some advice he gave me for yeast selection on my second all grain batch.  I also unveil my latest brewing contraption and a thanks for SteelJan for inspiration!  It's been busy, but fun, and very VERY tasty!  Cheers, Friends!
